<br>
They call it the UN. It's Headquarters is located in New York City. Most of the nations of the world are members. It is a medium that can be used to discuss hot topics, and try to work things out peacably. When war is unavoidable the UN sends in &quot;peacekeepers&quot; in an attemtpt to cool things down without the lose of human life.<br>
<br>
Meet Saddam Hussein. Altho a member of the UN Saddam Hussein is not trustworthy. He has agreed to all condintions in the past, and then after the fact breaks his word and does not meet the conditions he had previously agreed too.<br>
<br>
Meet George Bush. Now President of the United States. Sadam has been an issue for the 2 previous Presidents, one of which was George W. Bush's father. 12 years after the fact Saddam is still refusing to comply with actions he himself agreed too. George W. Bush finally decides enough is enough, and gives Saddam an ultimatum. Comply or Die. <br>
<br>
It looks as if Saddam is backed into a corner, and reluctantly he once again agrees to do allow whatever the west wants. He once again agrees to their terms. He has once again given into the west and is willing to open his country to neutral observers.<br>
<br>
This brings us to today. You gotta ask yourself, is it worth the lose of (worst case scenario) 75,000 lives to save 500 Million? You gotta ask yourself. To put that into perspective look at it like this. 1 guy is holding 6667 people hostage in a building that is lined with explosives. The man walks outside carrying the only detonator in his hand. From where you are you have a clean shot, and pulling the trigger will ensure that those 6667 people inside live to see another day, but unfortunatly their captor will die. All negotiations have failed, and all the maniac has left is stall tactics. Do you pull the trigger and save 6667 lives at the cost of one, or do you try to appeas the guy with the bomb and hope that somewhere down the line things can be worked out &quot;peacefully&quot;? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udeebius.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deebius</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 357<br> <font color=#333333>(9/26/02 1:15:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=972.topic&index=127>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> What people are in the building?<br>
